des:
Do you want to get stronger, healthier, and look super fine? Then the push-up challenge is the place to be!

With pushup challenge you can:
- Set daily goals
- Do 10 levels of challenges
- Keep track of your lifetime pushups
- Compete on the global leaderboard
- Set reminders to help you reach your goals (hourly/daily)
- Get Sexy

Challenge Guide:
- Level 1: 15 seconds of pushups
- Level 2: 30 seconds of pushups
- Level 3: 1 minute of pushups
- Each level after Level 3 adds an extra set of 1-minute pushups followed by 30 seconds of rest. Example Level 5 gives you 3 sets of 1-minute pushups, with each set followed by 30 seconds of rest. 

Pushup challenge will also prompt you to increase your goal as you grow stronger. 

Please consider rating Pushup Challenge, if you have any recommendations, feedback or questions please contact me at nate.lee.munk@gmail.com
